.TP
.BI \-\-config " PATH"
Path to config.toml.
Default:
.IR /etc/das\-backup/config.toml .
.TP
.BI \-\-sources " LABELS"
Comma-separated source labels.
Default: all.
.\"
.SS backup send
Send existing snapshots to targets.
.PP
.B btrdasd backup send
.RB [ \-\-config
.IR PATH ]
.RB [ \-\-targets
.IR LABELS ]
.TP
.BI \-\-config " PATH"
Path to config.toml.
Default:
.IR /etc/das\-backup/config.toml .
.TP
.BI \-\-targets " LABELS"
Comma-separated target labels.
Default: all mounted.
.\"
.SS backup boot\-archive
