.BI \-\-limit " N"
Number of recent runs to show.
Default: 10.
.\"
.SS restore file
Restore specific files from a snapshot.
.PP
.B btrdasd restore file
.I SNAPSHOT DEST FILE
.RI [ FILE .\|.\|.]
.TP
.I SNAPSHOT
Path to the snapshot directory.
.TP
.I DEST
Destination directory for restored files.
.TP
.I FILE
One or more file paths relative to the snapshot root (at least one required).
.\"
.SS restore snapshot
Restore an entire snapshot using btrfs send/receive or recursive copy.
.PP
.B btrdasd restore snapshot
.I SNAPSHOT DEST
.TP
